## SQL:
## Analysis of Issues

1. **`Using temporary; Using filesort`** on `UNION ALL` — the global `ORDER BY` + `LIMIT` forces MySQL to materialize the entire union before sorting, which is the most expensive step.
2. **`EXISTS` correlated subquery on `tag_thing`** — evaluated row-by-row for every candidate; converted to a pre-materialized `INNER JOIN` derived table.
3. **`JOIN user`** — the uuid predicate is evaluated after the join; pushing it into a derived table pre-filters users before joining.
4. **No early row pruning** — each branch sends all matching rows to the final sort; adding `ORDER BY … LIMIT` per branch caps the input to the outer sort at 20 rows maximum.

## Applied Optimizations

| Problem | Fix |
|---|---|
| Correlated `EXISTS` per row | Replace with `INNER JOIN` on a materialized `DISTINCT document_template_id` derived table |
| User uuid filter post-join | Push uuid `IN`/`NOT IN` into a derived table so filtering happens before the join |
| Whole-union filesort | Add `ORDER BY title ASC LIMIT 10` inside each branch; wrap in outer query for final sort |
| Redundant UNION temporary table scan | Outer `SELECT` over the wrapped union reduces the filesort to at most 20 rows |

## Optimized SQL

```sql
SELECT id, title FROM ((SELECT d.id, d.title FROM document_template d INNER JOIN (SELECT id FROM `user` WHERE uuid IN ('b60c5bfd-1ccb-40a3-a459-20998121f765','f2abfee7-c8a1-4540-9a0e-75921263650a')) u ON u.id = d.owner_id INNER JOIN (SELECT DISTINCT document_template_id FROM tag_thing WHERE tag_id = '9963ebcd-c834-4ff1-bdf5-229ef1b59204' AND deleted_at IS NULL) tt ON tt.document_template_id = d.id WHERE d.deleted_at IS NULL AND MATCH(d.title) AGAINST('Epaul' IN BOOLEAN MODE) > 0 AND d.title LIKE '%Epaul%' ORDER BY d.title ASC LIMIT 10) UNION ALL (SELECT d.id, d.title FROM document_template d INNER JOIN (SELECT id FROM `user` WHERE uuid NOT IN ('b60c5bfd-1ccb-40a3-a459-20998121f765','f2abfee7-c8a1-4540-9a0e-75921263650a')) u ON u.id = d.owner_id INNER JOIN (SELECT DISTINCT document_template_id FROM tag_thing WHERE tag_id = '9963ebcd-c834-4ff1-bdf5-229ef1b59204' AND deleted_at IS NULL) tt ON tt.document_template_id = d.id WHERE d.private = 0 AND d.deleted_at IS NULL AND MATCH(d.title) AGAINST('Epaul' IN BOOLEAN MODE) > 0 AND d.title LIKE '%Epaul%' ORDER BY d.title ASC LIMIT 10)) combined ORDER BY title ASC LIMIT 10 OFFSET 0
```

